2018年6月，Paradox Interactive以750万美元的固定价格收购了《{{tsl|en|Shadowrun Returns||Shadowrun Returns}}》和《{{tsl|en|BattleTech (video game)||BattleTech}}》的开发商{{tsl|en|Harebrained Schemes||Harebrained Schemes}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.paradoxinteractive.com/en/paradox-interactive-to-acquire-seattle-based-harebrained-schemes/|title=Paradox Interactive to acquire Seattle-based Harebrained Schemes|date=June 5, 2018|website=Paradox Interactive|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180606155156/https://www.paradoxinteractive.com/en/paradox-interactive-to-acquire-seattle-based-harebrained-schemes/|archive-date=6 June 2018|access-date=2018-06-05}}</ref>。

